{"tid":914550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"IOS 終於可以自製WhatsApp Stickers！","createTime":"2018-11-24T11:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T18:25:13.000Z","uid":223797,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3f7dbe3ce941d4357efa98924d8a41dfca82d7","tid":914550,"uid":223797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟不才，應朋友訴求上星期整左隻 iOS app 幫大家可以自製WhatsApp Sticker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身想等我第二個bug fix version 出到街先同大家講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但PK 蘋果唔批我個新 version ，話咩大多同類型app 又話要依賴其他app 先得咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(DKLM sticker 緊係要WhatsApp 先用到，佢都on99999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n依家個app隨時有機會俾人落架，大家想自製whatsapp sticker就down 左先<br />\n(down 左既app 蘋果落我架都影響唔到你用)<br />\n<br />\nMyStickers:<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fmystickers%2Fid1442605866%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=pMSCnlU2dnyOAO5ZSdGKPG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=95f0c1c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/191519_c3b50018bb5e413bb73e63f3dd6a333b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F191519_c3b50018bb5e413bb73e63f3dd6a333b.png&h=cdb0146f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/24/191524_bb6389c7355c5ad896e3919765f43963.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F24%2F191524_bb6389c7355c5ad896e3919765f43963.png&h=8cf2bd65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個version 有bug ：<br />\n- 入唔齊name 同 icon 圖會彈app<br />\n- 入太多太大既圖會爆memory 彈app<br />\n- 圖 file size 大過 100KB 會用jpeg 壓縮冇左透明底<br />\n<br />\n祝大家自製到sticker 唔洗俾android fd 屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9480c8ba9541bbfc91ce676b16181a992ecdd649","tid":914550,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"可以消背景？"},{"pid":"af4ee32091dbbc9079eecff4e6f99d2925aa49a7","tid":914550,"uid":15572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c50cca7e3f06b249b7945bd09a36d44ce9aac27","tid":914550,"uid":223797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"冇消背景功能，整唔切，只可上傳到sticker落WhatsApp"},{"pid":"56b5c7e528da2c79c44ce23c2a9c8935e80f4a5f","tid":914550,"uid":53027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"冇得cut圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a5882dd29cdac0931f0272eb3bad67ded26902","tid":914550,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eecdba1b7498253d014ff326f6d7c2c0fa31122","tid":914550,"uid":223